  "limitations": [
    "This is a deliberately minimal Phase 0 route and API, not the production cockpit or owner authentication system.",
    "The deterministic in-process provider runs inside the task container and makes no network request; an owner-operated real-provider smoke is separate evidence.",
    "Restart reconciliation proves the idle container identity and pauses the run before cleanup. In-flight Pi RPC process reattachment is not implemented in this prototype.",
    "The deterministic in-process provider exercises real Pi RPC without network or credentials; remote provider transport is outside this result.",
